{% extends 'emails/email_base.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}

    <h2>Reset Your Credentials</h2>

    <p>We received a request to reset your password for the secure document portal linked to <strong>{{ firmName }}</strong>.</p>

    <p>Please click the button below to set your new password. Clicking this link will initiate a cryptographic keypair generation inside your browser to rebuild your secure workspace profile:</p>

    <center>
        <button href="{{ resetUrl }}" class="button">Reset My Password</button>
    </center>

    <div class="notice">
        <strong>Notice on E2EE Data Restores:</strong>
        Since your documents are end-to-end encrypted, resetting a forgotten password will regenerate your security identity keys. If you are a staff member, your account will temporarily go into approval status so an Administrator can securely re-wrap past files using your new credentials.
    </div>

    <p class="secondary-text">
        This reset link is valid for exactly 1 hour. If you did not request this update, you can safely ignore this email; your existing keys and account access remain fully locked and secure.
    </p>
{% endblock %}
